==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: goof-off
<hw>goof-off</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person who habitually shirks his
duties or avoids work; an idle worthless person.</def>
<mark>[Informal]</mark> ⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> goldbrick, ne'er-do-well, good-for-nothing,
good-for-naught.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> + <source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>goofproof</ent>⟦br⟧
